						<summary>

						<p>On pillar No. 9 in the compound of the Taluk Office.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated Śaka 11[3]0, corresponding to A.D. 1208-1209.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register a lamp-stand weighing 42 <hi rend="italic">vīsas</hi> and a gift of land for maintaining a lamp in the Bhīmēśvara temple.</p>						

